						               													<description>A board game designed to be a suspenseful adventure of exploration, strategy, and gambling where you are immersed in epic battles.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Action Battle System&amp;#10;Our interactive Battle System brings you directly into the fight itself, where the dice represent real-time actions your hero is performing&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Our D8 custom Battle Dice include the following die faces: Attack (x2), Defend (x2), Roll, Jump, Slide, Wild.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Mist Monsters&amp;#10;As your Hero embarks on their journey, they will encounter monsters from the Mist (included in the core game).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Fog Monsters&amp;#10;Once your Hero is strong enough, they can begin Venturing the Fog. Lurking there are fiercer, more vile monsters (included in the extended game).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Gambling&amp;#10;Stay constantly engaged, wagering currency while other players battle monsters. Gamble correctly and use the newfound currency to your advantage.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Exploration&amp;#10;The expansive swamp is different each time you play. Venture deep into the unknown, carving you own path to collect treasures and defeat monsters along the way.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Gearing Up&amp;#10;Defeat monster and loot them for better armor and weapons. Be rewarded with additional loot by risking more challenging fights along the way.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
